text: Is it weird that as soon as I saw this headline I started humming the Serial theme?
Curious, has anyone else been experiencing fairly frequent spottiness in the internet lately? I can't reliably stream music online much anymore.  I'm wondering if it's my machine.
which network are you on, where are you sitting?
It doesn't matter which network for me, they're all the same when it's spotty. And I'm at my desk.
try hardwiring. try sitting next to the access point.
investigation found a chrome process taking 15% CPU, which is a little high. Bandwidth down was 70+MB, up was ~20. Pings at 12-28ms. I recommend Chrome restart and call me in the morning.
